《光环》是一首当代[[节奏|慢游]]强力情歌<ref name="ign"/><ref name="DS"/>且包含了[[流行音乐|流行]]的制作<ref name="billcrit">{{Cite journal |title=Lily Allen The Singer Speaks Out On EMI, Endorsement Deals, And How She Deals With Perez And The Paparazzi |volume=121 |issue=2|date=2009-01-17|work=Billboard|publisher=[[Nielsen_Company|Nielsen Business Media]] |page=34 |issn=0006-2510 |last=Williams |first=Christian}}</ref>。它还有[[福音音乐|福音]]和[[靈魂樂|靈魂樂]]的元素<ref name="ign"/><ref name="thui"/>。这首歌由[[钢琴|钢琴]]<ref name="jam">{{cite web |url=http://jam.canoe.ca/Music/Artists/B/Beyonce/AlbumReviews/2008/11/18/7453821-sun.html |title=Album Review: Beyonce I Am... Sasha Fierce |first=Darryl |last=Sterdan |publisher=Jam!. Sun Media |date=2008-11-18 |accessdate=2011-01-15 |archive-date=2012-07-09 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20120709071101/http://jam.canoe.ca/Music/Artists/B/Beyonce/AlbumReviews/2008/11/18/7453821-sun.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[鍵盤樂器|键盘]]<ref name="sheet"/>、[[鼓|大鼓]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/content_display/reviews/albums/e3ifc7bb2290700c27fc478bd2c3ff3dde9 |title=I Am... Sasha Fierce |first=Mariel |last=Concepcion |work=Billboard |publisher=Nielsen Business Media |date=2008-11-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090529065427/http://www.billboard.com/bbcom/content_display/reviews/albums/e3ifc7bb2290700c27fc478bd2c3ff3dde9 |archivedate=2009-05-29 |accessdate=2011-12-31 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>、[[合成器|合成器]]<ref name="guardian">{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2008/nov/14/beyonce-i-am-sasha-fierce|title=Pop review: Beyoncé, I Am ... Sasha Fierce|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|publisher=Guardian Media Group|accessdate=2010-12-15|date=2008-11-14|first=Alexis|last=Petridis|archive-date=2013-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130930215931/http://www.theguardian.com/music/2008/nov/14/beyonce-i-am-sasha-fierce|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[弦樂器|弦乐]]和[[打擊樂器|打击]]<ref name="ew2"/>的乐器作为伴奏。那如瀑布般下落的钢琴声<ref>{{cite web |last=Elan |first=Priya |url=http://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/beyonce-4-first-listen-773727 |title=Beyonce, '4' – First Listen |work=[[NME|NME]] |publisher=IPC Media |date=2011-06-10 |accessdate=2011-12-11 |archive-date=2017-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170226214322/http://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/beyonce-4-first-listen-773727 |dead-url=no }}</ref>伴随着打击乐器的[[拍子|拍子]]轮流在[[鼓掌|拍掌声]]和跺脚声之间交替着<ref name="ew2"/><ref name="jam"/><ref name="ign">{{cite web|accessdate=2011-01-15|url=http://music.ign.com/articles/933/933019p1.html|title=Beyonce – I Am... Sasha Fierce: The two sides of Ms. Beyoncé fight for your attention|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]. [[News_Corporation|News Corporation]]|date=2008-11-22|first=Spence|last=D|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110628214443/http://music.ign.com/articles/933/933019p1.html|archivedate=2011-06-28}}</ref>。《光环》由[[A大调|A大调]]的[[拍号|4/4拍]]写成，[[速度_(音乐)|速度]]是每分钟84拍<ref name="sheet"/>。其{{le|和弦进程|Chord progression}}是以A–Bm–F{{music|sharp}}m–D为基础，并以同样的[[副歌|正副歌形式]]而写成<ref name="sheet">{{cite AV media notes|title=Halo – Beyoncé Beyoncé Digital Sheet Music |type=Digital Download |publisher=Musicnotes.com Hal Leonard Corporation|id=MN0072471}}</ref>。碧昂丝演唱时的音域在[[C♯_(音名)|C♯3]]到[[F♯_(音名)|F♯5]]的[[假音|假音]]之间<ref name="sheet"/>，也包含了{{le|拉腔|Melisma}}<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2010/12/26/arts/music/26browne.html |title=Trilling Songbirds Clip Their Wings |first=David |last=Browne |work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |publisher=The New York Times Company |date=2010-12-24 |accessdate=2011-12-19 |archive-date=2012-08-25 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6ABcqdJYG?url=http://www.nytimes.com/2010/12/26/arts/music/26browne.html?_r=2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>并承受破音<ref name="sheet"/>。她在歌唱时使用[[裝飾音|裝飾音]]、有[[抖音|抖音]]的高音部分和[[顫音_(音樂)|颤音]]<ref name="ign"/>——在两个接近的音符之间有快的变化，通常是一个[[半音|半音]]或者[[全音|全音]]的相距。该编曲还由[[交響曲|交響曲]]的[[強弱法|渐强程度]]和电子[[銜接_(音樂)|重音]]所构成<ref name="thui">{{cite news |url=http://www.chron.com/entertainment/music/article/CD-showcases-Beyonce-s-split-personality-1675646.php |title=Album Review: Beyonce I Am... Sasha Fierce |first=Joey |last=Guerra |work=[[Houston_Chronicle|Houston Chronicle]] |publisher=Hearst Corporation |date=2008-11-17 |accessdate=2011-01-16 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6fnCnCDYA?url=http://www.chron.com/entertainment/music/article/CD-showcases-Beyonce-s-split-personality-1675646.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在歌词中，碧昂丝以寬廣的胸懷表達了對自己神聖戀人的無微不至的愛情<ref name="jam"/><ref name="thui"/><ref name="pitch">{{cite web |url=http://pitchfork.com/reviews/albums/12462-i-am-sasha-fierce/ |title=Album Reviews: Beyoncé: I Am... Sasha Fierce |first=Ryan |last=Dombal |publisher=[[Pitchfork_Media|Pitchfork Media]] |date=2008-11-21 |accessdate=2011-01-15 |archive-date=2011-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110102133549/http://pitchfork.com/reviews/albums/12462-i-am-sasha-fierce/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她说：「[《光环》]有如天使般……就好像當你聽到這首歌的瞬間就能看到[天使的]臉龐。[這首歌的歌詞]基本上表達的是我築起心牆，而當我看到你頭頂的光環時，你卻讓我卸下了心防，這一切真的很美。」<ref name="Iamplat">{{cite video |people=[[Beyoncé|Knowles, Beyoncé]] |date=2009 |title=I Am... Sasha Fierce ''[Platinum Edition]'' |format=DVD |publisher=Columbia Records |accessdate=2011-04-12 |time=9:10 to 10:50 |url=http://www.amazon.com/Am-Sasha-Fierce-Platinum-Edition-Tracks/dp/B002LBGBR2 |archive-date=2012-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120417023600/http://www.amazon.com/Am-Sasha-Fierce-Platinum-Edition-Tracks/dp/B002LBGBR2 |dead-url=no }} {{Wayback|url=http://www.amazon.com/Am-Sasha-Fierce-Platinum-Edition-Tracks/dp/B002LBGBR2 |date=20120417023600 }}</ref>歌曲刚刚开始的钢琴声、鼓掌和跺脚声，会给歌曲營造了靈性的氛圍<ref name="jam"/><ref name="ign"/>，之后碧昂丝唱道：「Remember those walls I built? Well, baby, they're tumbling down」（大意：还记得我筑起的高墙吗？亲爱的，它们已然倒塌）<ref name="thui"/>。歌曲前奏以低音區演唱，隨著歌曲進行，聲音逐漸加強<ref name="eheh"/>。在导歌中，她重复地唱着：「Everywhere I'm looking now, I'm surrounded by your embrace, baby I can see your halo, you know you're my saving grace, you're everything I need and more, it's written all over your face」（大意：我眼前每一個所見之處，都被你双臂紧紧围绕，宝贝我看见你身上散发的光环，你知道吗？你是我的守护神，你是我需要的一切，甚至更多，这全部写在了你的脸上）<ref name="rap1"/><ref name="DS">{{cite web |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/singlesreviews/a147168/beyonce-halo.html |title=Beyoncé: 'Halo' |publisher=Digital Spy. Hachette Filipacchi (UK) Ltd |first=David |last=Balls |date=2009-04-13 |accessdate=2009-04-16 |archive-date=2009-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091206101431/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/singlesreviews/a147168/beyonce-halo.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。碧昂丝接着在[[副歌|副歌]]里重复吟唱着「光环」一词<ref name="eheh">{{cite web |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1597718/beyonces-i-sasha-fierce-album-preview.jhtml |title=Beyonce Album Preview: I Am ... Sasha Fierce Shines Light On B's Alter Ego |first=Jennifer |last=Vineyard |publisher=MTV News. MTV Networks |date=2008-10-23 |accessdate=2011-01-15 |archive-date=2012-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120209055707/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1597718/beyonces-i-sasha-fierce-album-preview.jhtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>；副歌的第三次也是最後一次重複由一串1980年代風格的鼓點引出，並以[[掃弦|掃弦]]和打擊樂作結<ref name="ew2">{{cite web |first=Michael |last=Slezak |url=http://popwatch.ew.com/2009/01/07/beyonce-vs-beyo/ |title=Beyonce vs. Beyonce! ('Diva' vs. 'Halo'!) Weigh in! |date=2010-01-07 |accessdate=2010-05-25 |work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |publisher=Time Inc |archive-date=2010-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100715153911/http://popwatch.ew.com/2009/01/07/beyonce-vs-beyo/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/blogs/chartblog/2009/04/beyonce_halo.shtml |title=Beyoncé – 'Halo' |first=Fraser |last=McAlpine |publisher=[[BBC_Online|BBC Online]]. BBC |date=2009-04-01 |accessdate=2012-01-16 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6fnD6afmM?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/blogs/chartblog/2009/04/beyonce_halo.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==发行==
2008年，碧昂絲在美國發行雙重首發單曲《[[如果我是男生|如果我是男生]]》和《{{le|單身女郎 (定情戒)|Single Ladies (Put a Ring on It)}}》，原計劃在此之後于美國同時發行《光环》和《{{le|自我意识 (歌曲)|Ego (Beyoncé_song)|自我意识}}》<ref name="rap1"/>。但是《自我意识》的发行被取消而取而代之的是《{{le|玩美女神|Diva (Beyoncé_song)}}》<ref name="shot">{{cite web |url=http://www.rap-up.com/2008/12/23/videos-beyonce-halo-diva/ |title=Videos: Beyoncé – 'Halo' & 'Diva' |accessdate=2011-12-29 |work=Rap-Up |publisher=Devin Lazerine |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304114909/http://www.rap-up.com/2008/12/23/videos-beyonce-halo-diva/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《光环》与《完美女神》出自《双面碧昂丝》分別收錄於專輯不同的兩部分中，意在表現碧昂絲本人雙面的性格，即這張專輯表達的主題<ref name="billcrit"/><ref name="mtv1">{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1596842/20081010/knowles_beyonce.jhtml|title=Beyonce's Very Different New Videos: One Has Dancing, One Has Relationship Problems|last=Vineyard|first=Jennifer|date=2008-10-13|publisher=MTV News. MTV Networks|accessdate=2010-12-15|archive-date=2012-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103114517/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1596842/beyonce-releases-two-very-different-new-music-videos.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Boston"/>。專輯的兩個不同的部分分別收錄抒情謠曲和動感快節奏舞曲，以此來表現碧昂絲性格的雙面性<ref name="eheh"/><ref name="Boston"/>。《光环》于2009年1月20日由音乐世界娱乐（Music World Entertainment）和[[哥伦比亚唱片|哥伦比亚唱片]]发送给[[當代流行音樂類型電台|当代流行电台]]的表演曲目<ref name="FQ">{{cite web |url=http://www.fmqb.com/Article.asp?id=69239 |title=Available for Airplay: 1/20 Mainstream |work=Friday Morning Quarterback |publisher=Friday Morning Quarterback Album Report, Inc. and Mediaspan Online Services |accessdate=2010-05-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110720210133/http://fmqb.com/Article.asp?id=69239 |archivedate=2011-07-20 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，而《玩美女神》分类于{{le|节奏当代音乐类型|rhythmic contemporary|节奏当代}}和{{le|城市当代音乐类型|urban contemporary|城市当代}}电台的表演曲目<ref>{{cite web |url=http://gfa.radioandrecords.com/publishGFA/GFANextPage.asp?sDate=01/20/2009&Format=5 |title=R&R :: Going For Adds :: Urban |publisher=Radio & Records. VNU Media |accessdate=2011-12-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110719062444/http://gfa.radioandrecords.com/publishGFA/GFANextPage.asp?sDate=01%2F20%2F2009&Format=5 |archivedate=2011-07-19 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://gfa.radioandrecords.com/publishGFA/GFANextPage.asp?sDate=01/20/2009&Format=5 |title=R&R :: Going For Adds :: Rhythmic |publisher=Radio & Records. VNU Media |accessdate=2011-12-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110719062444/http://gfa.radioandrecords.com/publishGFA/GFANextPage.asp?sDate=01%2F20%2F2009&Format=5 |archivedate=2011-07-19 }}</ref>。[[迷你专辑|迷你专辑]]包含了《光环》{{le|电台剪辑|Radio edit}}版本和四首[[重混|重混]]版本，并于2009年4月14日发行<ref name="usep">{{cite web |url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/halo-single-remixes/id311092222 |title=Halo (Single & Remixes) by Beyoncé |publisher=[[iTunes_Store|iTunes Store]] (US). [[Apple_Inc|Apple Inc]] |accessdate=2011-12-29 |archive-date=2012-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120401093944/http://itunes.apple.com/us/album/halo-single-remixes/id311092222 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2009年2月20日，《光环》在澳大利亚<ref name="aussi">{{cite web |url=https://itunes.apple.com/au/album/halo-single/id305150078 |title=Halo – Single by Beyoncé |publisher=iTunes Store (Australia). Apple Inc |accessdate=2011-12-29 |archive-date=2012-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121110180039/https://itunes.apple.com/au/album/halo-single/id305150078 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、纽西兰<ref>{{cite web |url=https://itunes.apple.com/nz/album/halo-single/id305150078 |title=Halo – Single by Beyoncé |publisher=iTunes Store (New Zealand). Apple Inc |accessdate=2011-12-29 |archive-date=2013-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131208082051/https://itunes.apple.com/nz/album/halo-single/id305150078 |dead-url=no }}</ref>和加拿大<ref>{{cite web |url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/halo-single-remixes/id311092222 |title=Halo – Single by Beyoncé |publisher=iTunes Store (Canada). Apple Inc |accessdate=2011-12-29 |archive-date=2012-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120401093944/http://itunes.apple.com/us/album/halo-single-remixes/id311092222 |dead-url=no }}</ref>以[[数位音乐下载|数位下载]]的方式将两首单曲发行，包括了《單身女郎(定情戒)》的重混版本——这首歌还以数字迷你专辑[[单曲|12cm单曲]]和[[黑胶唱片|黑胶唱片]]的形式于2009年4月14日发行<ref name="canep">{{cite web |url=https://itunes.apple.com/ca/album/halo-single-remixes/id311092222 |title=Halo (Single & Remixes) by Beyoncé |publisher=iTunes Store (Canada). Apple Inc |accessdate=2011-12-29 |archive-date=2014-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140710045525/https://itunes.apple.com/ca/album/halo-single-remixes/id311092222 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.amazon.ca/dp/B0021CDG74 |title=Halo (Vinyl)| accessdate=2010-06-08|publisher=[[Amazon.com|Amazon.com]] (Canada)}}</ref>。在法国，它于2009年3月20日以独立的数位下载单曲的方式发行<ref name="am.fr">{{cite web|url=http://www.amazon.fr/dp/B0026UT6IY|title=Halo|accessdate=2010-06-08|publisher=Amazon.com (France)|archive-date=2021-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210210230356/https://www.amazon.fr/dp/B0026UT6IY|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在同一日，《光环》与《玩美女神》的专辑版本共同数位化于欧洲大陆<ref name="eud">{{cite web |url=https://itunes.apple.com/be/music-video/halo/id338528366 |title=Halo – Single by Beyoncé |publisher=iTunes Store (Belgium). Apple Inc |accessdate=2011-12-29 |archive-date=2017-03-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170319022910/https://itunes.apple.com/be/music-video/halo/id338528366 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其中包括德国<ref>{{cite web |url=https://itunes.apple.com/de/album/halo-single/id307743593 |accessdate=2011-07-09 |publisher=iTunes Store (Germany). Apple Inc |title=Halo – Single von Beyoncé – Halo |archive-date=2012-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121112201634/https://itunes.apple.com/de/album/halo-single/id307743593 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，它还在当地以[[CD单曲|CD单曲]]于4月3日发行，并以黑胶单曲的方式于2009年4月12日发行<ref name="gercdd">{{cite web|url=http://www.amazon.de/Halo-Beyonc%C3%A9/dp/B001UEFH4O/ref=sr_1_1?s=music&ie=UTF8&qid=1325082283&sr=1-1 |title=Halo (Single )|accessdate=2011-12-29 |publisher=Amazon.com (Germany)}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.amazon.de/Halo-Vinyl-Single-Beyonce/dp/B0021CDG74/ref=sr_1_1?s=music&ie=UTF8&qid=1364155068&sr=1-1 |title=Halo (Vinyl Single) |accessdate=2011-12-29 |publisher=Amazon.com (Germany)}}</ref>。在英国，《光环》以数位迷你专辑于2009年4月13日发行，其中包括了歌曲专辑版本和三首重混版本<ref name="ukep">{{cite web |url=http://www.amazon.co.uk/Halo/dp/B0022VNGQU/ref=sr_1_fkmr0_1?s=dmusic&ie=UTF8&qid=1364155152&sr=1-1-fkmr0 |title=Halo – EP by Beyoncé |publisher=Amazon.com (UK) |accessdate=2011-12-29 |archive-date=2021-02-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210210230409/https://www.amazon.co.uk/Halo/dp/B0022VNGQU/ref=sr_1_fkmr0_1?s=dmusic&ie=UTF8&qid=1364155152&sr=1-1-fkmr0 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="sony">{{cite web |url=http://www.sonymusic.co.uk/releases/903/ |title=Releases – Beyoncé Knowles – Halo |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090406031842/http://www.sonymusic.co.uk/releases/903/ |archivedate=2009-04-06 |publisher=Sony Music UK. [[Sony_Music_Entertainment|Sony Music Entertainment]] |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2017-01-15 }}</ref>。

==凱莉·克萊森的指责==
在完成《光环》之后，泰德与[[凱莉·克萊森|凱莉·克萊森]]共同创作她的第四张专辑《{{le|无可就要|All I Ever Wanted (album)}}》，并一同创作《{{le|爱已成往事|Already Gone (Kelly Clarkson song)}}》这首歌曲<ref name="CBC"/>。当这首歌发行后，评论家特别注意到这听起来与《光环》相似<ref name="MTV1"/>。但是克莱森起初未意识到两首歌之间的相同之处<ref name="MTV2"/>。她最终仔细聽录制时才发现它们两者的相似；那些相同最显著的是它的伴奏，例如两者都使用了忧郁的钢琴声、响亮的鼓声和拍掌声<ref name="MTV1">{{cite web |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1617011/kelly-clarkson-i-didnt-rip-off-beyonce.jhtml |title=Think Kelly Clarkson's 'Already Gone' Sounds Like Beyonce's 'Halo?' So Does Kelly ... |last=Montgomery |first=James |date=2009-07-27 |publisher=MTV News. MTV Networks |accessdate=2011-12-25 |archive-date=2012-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103074107/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1617011/kelly-clarkson-i-didnt-rip-off-beyonce.jhtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。克莱森尝试去阻止《爱已成往事》出现在《无可就要》里，但是这个决定已经无法控制，因为当时《双面碧昂丝》释出时，她的专辑早已開始印刷生產<ref name="CBC"/>。她指责泰德在《光环》和《爱已成往事》之间使用了相同的编曲，并抱怨人们可能会错误地认为她抄袭碧昂丝的歌曲<ref name="CBC">{{cite news |first=Sarah |last=Liss |title=American Idyll |url=http://www.cbc.ca/arts/music/story/2009/07/24/f-kelly-clarkson-new-album.html |publisher=CBC News. Canadian Broadcasting Corporation |date=2009-07-27 |accessdate=2010-05-19 |archive-date=2009-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090727141459/http://www.cbc.ca/arts/music/story/2009/07/24/f-kelly-clarkson-new-album.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

克莱森极其生气地在手机里与泰德对峙<ref name="CBC"/>。在回应中，泰德评论道他从来没有给两个艺人相同的编曲，之后她批评这样是「令人受伤和荒唐的」<ref name="T resp"/>。他断言道《爱已成往事》和《光环》两者的概念、旋律和歌词是完全不同的<ref name="T resp"/>。泰德称《爱已称往事》是他有史以来创作的最好的一首歌曲，并挑战人们「去聽那两首情歌并抒发他们自己的想法」<ref name="T resp">{{cite web |title=Ryan Tedder responds to Kelly Clarkson/Beyoncé controversy |url=http://music-mix.ew.com/2009/07/29/ryan-tedder-clarkson-beyonce-statement/ |date=2009-07-29 |first=Simon |last=Vozick-Levinson |work=Entertainment Weekly |publisher=Time Inc |accessdate=2010-05-19 |archive-date=2012-07-08 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68zmIG0Av?url=http://music-mix.ew.com/2009/07/29/ryan-tedder-clarkson-beyonce-statement/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。克莱森试图以尊重碧昂丝的原因阻止她的唱片公司[[RCA唱片|RCA]]将《爱已成往事》作为单曲<ref name="rolli">{{cite web|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/clarksons-already-gone-video-debuts-despite-kellys-protests-20090727|title=Clarkson's "Already Gone" Video Debuts, Despite Kelly's Protests|work=[[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]]|publisher=Wenner Media LLC|accessdate=2011-03-29|date=2009-07-27|archive-date=2012-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120731044746/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/clarksons-already-gone-video-debuts-despite-kellys-protests-20090727|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但他们反对她的意愿并照常发行<ref name="CBC" />。她说：「這就是我不能控制的事情之一。我已经制作了我的专辑。在那个时候，唱片公司想对它做什么都行。」<ref>{{cite web |title=Kelly Clarkson's 'Already Gone': Does it really rip off Beyonce's 'Halo'? Diva crisis! |url=http://music-mix.ew.com/2009/07/27/kelly-clarkson-beyonce/ |date=2009-07-27 |first=Leah |last=Greenblatt |work=Entertainment Weekly |publisher=Time Inc |accessdate=2010-12-29 |archive-date=2011-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110109205111/http://music-mix.ew.com/2009/07/27/kelly-clarkson-beyonce/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>她之后告诉{{le|MTV新闻|MTV News}}的詹姆士·蒙哥馬利（{{lang|en|James Montgomery}}）《爱已成往事》和《光环》听起来如此相似让她很不舒服，但是欣慰的是它们至少有不同的演唱旋律<ref name="MTV2">{{cite web |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1621839/20090918/clarkson_kelly.jhtml |title=Kelly Clarkson To Put Ryan Tedder Drama To Bed On Upcoming Tour |last=Montgomery |first=James |date=2009-09-18 |publisher=MTV News. MTV Networks |accessdate=2011-12-25 |archive-date=2012-07-08 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68zmOP3HH?url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1621839/kelly-clarkson-put-ryan-tedder-drama-bed.jhtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==樂評==
===杂志评价===
《光环》发行之后获得了评论家的普遍好评，他们均称赞碧昂丝的演唱表现。《[[告示牌_(杂志)|告示牌]]》杂志的克里斯蒂安·威廉斯（{{lang|en|Christian Williams}}）写道《光环》的流行乐的声音应该让其成为榜单的榜首<ref name="billcrit"/>。他补充到说它可以与《{{le|蔓延的爱|Bleeding Love}}》形成对比，但是总结道《光环》「如根據其本身特點的话，就比《蔓延的爱》的水平更高更好」<ref name="billcrit"/>。《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》的迈克尔·斯莱扎克（{{lang|en|Michael Slezak}}）称《光环》为「一首完全地美丽和完美的制作单曲」，并有潜质与《{{le|疯狂爱恋|Crazy in Love (Beyoncé song)}}》和《[[绝无仅有|绝无仅有]]》一样获得巨大的商业成功<ref name="ew2"/>。《[[休斯敦纪事报|休斯敦纪事报]]》的乔伊·格拉（{{lang|en|Joey Guerra}}）写道它立刻成为《双面碧昂丝》的出众单曲<ref name="thui"/>。《[[影音俱樂部|影音俱樂部]]》的马托斯·米開朗基羅（{{lang|en|Matos Michaelangelo}}）称赞《光环》那「流行且广泛的」旋律，并评价碧昂丝有「宏伟的才华」<ref>{{cite news|first=Michaelangelo|last=Matos|url=http://www.avclub.com/articles/beyonce-i-am-sasha-fierce,6733/|title=Music – Album Review – Beyoncé: 'I Am... Sasha Fierce'|work=[[The_A.V._Club|The A.V. Club]]|publisher=[[The_Onion|The Onion]]|date=2008-11-17|accessdate=2011-09-12|archive-date=2012-06-07|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68EcMio4D?url=http://www.avclub.com/articles/beyonce-i-am-sasha-fierce,6733/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{le|E!网络|E! Online}}的珍妮弗·卡迪（{{lang|en|Jennifer Cady}}）写道这首歌应该出现在一张浪漫的[[混音带|混音带]]里<ref name="perf">{{cite web|url=http://uk.eonline.com/news/new_videos_from_beyonceacuteand_sasha/74676|title=New Videos From Beyoncé...and Sasha Fierce!|first=Jennifer|last=Cady|publisher=E! Online. NBCUniversal|date=2008-12-23|accessdate=2011-09-13|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/624yQ1ad2?url=http://www.eonline.com/news/new_videos_from_beyonceacuteand_sasha/74676|archivedate=2011-09-30|deadurl=yes}}</ref>，还有MTV新闻的詹姆士·蒙哥馬利认为《光环》那「催人泪下的力量」而告诉了「碧昂丝那为人不知的一面」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1630462/beyonces-road-grammys-proves-fierce-diva.jhtml|title=Beyonce's Road To The Grammys Proves She Is A Fierce Diva|publisher=MTV News. MTV Networks|first=James|last=Montgomery|date=2010-01-25|accessdate=2011-11-28|archive-date=2012-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121104183437/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1630462/beyonces-road-grammys-proves-fierce-diva.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[Pitchfork_Media|Pitchfork Media]]的萊恩·敦渤（{{lang|en|Ryan Dombal}}）写道碧昂丝的演唱方式是「尖厉且毫無遮蔽的」，使人想起[[席琳·狄翁|席琳·狄翁]]的风格<ref name="pitch">{{cite web|url=http://pitchfork.com/reviews/albums/12462-i-am-sasha-fierce/ |title=Album Reviews: Beyoncé: I Am... Sasha Fierce |first=Ryan|last=Dombal |publisher=[[Pitchfork_Media|Pitchfork Media]] |date=2008-11-21 |accessdate=2011-01-15}}</ref>。

尽管《[[波士顿环球报|波士顿环球报]]》的詹姆斯·里德（{{lang|en|James Reed}}）称情歌有着「普通的歌词」，但他依然写道《光环》是碧昂丝录制的「最能唤起美好情感的强力情歌」，并将它与[[音樂製作人|音樂製作人]]和词曲作家[[菲尔·斯佩克特|菲尔·斯佩克特]]在{{le|Wall of Sound|Wall of Sound}}调音台录制的作品作出比较<ref name="Boston">{{Cite news |url=http://www.boston.com/ae/music/articles/2008/11/17/beyonceacute_branches_out/?page=full |title=Beyoncé branches out – The Boston Globe |publisher=The New York Times Company |work=The Boston Globe |date=2008-11-17 |accessdate=2009-11-30 |first=James |last=Reed |archive-date=2012-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121112072811/http://www.boston.com/ae/music/articles/2008/11/17/beyonceacute_branches_out/?page=full |dead-url=no }}</ref>。评论家特别强调了《光环》和蕾哈娜的《{{le|小雨伞|Umbrella (song)}}》之间的相同之处；《[[衛報|衛報]]》的亞歷克西斯·彼得里迪斯（{{lang|en|Alexis Petridis}}）谈到《光环》同样有「冷冰冰的合成声、高潮时的惊吓动态和相同地重复着副歌」<ref name="guardian">{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2008/nov/14/beyonce-i-am-sasha-fierce|title=Pop review: Beyoncé, I Am ... Sasha Fierce|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|publisher=Guardian Media Group|accessdate=2010-12-15|date=2008-11-14|first=Alexis|last=Petridis}}</ref>。MTV新闻的珍妮弗·万亚尔德（{{lang|en|Jennifer Vineyard}}）也有类似的观点<ref name="eheh">{{cite web| url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1597718/beyonces-i-sasha-fierce-album-preview.jhtml |title=Beyonce Album Preview: I Am ... Sasha Fierce Shines Light On B's Alter Ego |first=Jennifer |last=Vineyard |publisher=MTV News. MTV Networks |date=2008-10-23 |accessdate=2011-01-15}}</ref>，而《[[Time_Out|Time Out]]》布朗·迪克雷申佐（{{lang|en|Brent DiCrescenzo}}）將《光環》視為一个「[[贝蒂·米勒|贝蒂·米勒]]的重现——《小雨伞》的圣歌等级，举起那救世主般的主题」<ref name="hint"/>。数码间谍的尼可·李維（{{lang|en|Nick Levine}}）称《光环》为一个《小雨伞》和路易斯《蔓延的爱》的「震撼人心的混合」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/albumreviews/a136159/beyonce-i-am-sasha-fierce.html |title=Music – Album Review – Beyoncé: 'I Am... Sasha Fierce' |first=Nick |last=Levine |publisher=Digital Spy. Hachette Filipacchi (UK) Ltd |date=2008-11-17 |accessdate=2011-01-15 |archive-date=2012-06-07 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68EcLrZGA?url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/albumreviews/a136159/beyonce-i-am-sasha-fierce.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。相同网站的大卫·鲍尔斯写道：「《光环》是由《蔓延的爱》所塑造的当代强力情歌……路易斯可以演繹得更好吗？当然，這只是一個仁者見仁智者見智的問題，但杰斯太太似乎沒有留下许多改進的餘地。」<ref name="DS"/>

===奖项与表彰===
《光环》获得了{{le|2009年城市音乐奖|Urban Music Awards}}最佳单曲的提名<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.urbanmusicawards.net/us_news.php?id=108&start=0&limit=10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090509082404/http://www.urbanmusicawards.net/us_news.php?id=108&start=0&limit=10 |archivedate=2009-05-09 |title=Urban Music Awards |publisher=Urban Music Awards |accessdate=2010-05-30 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，和2009年[[青少年票選獎|青少年票選獎]]的音樂選擇獎：情歌提名<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/awards/2009/06/teen-choice-awards-2009-nominees.html|title=Teen Choice Awards 2009 nominees|publisher=Tribune Company|work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|date=2009-06-15|accessdate=2013-03-23|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6FL37oECa?url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/awards/2009/06/teen-choice-awards-2009-nominees.html|archivedate=2013-03-23|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。它赢得了[[2009年MTV歐洲音樂大獎|2009年MTV歐洲音樂大獎]]的[[2009年MTV歐洲音樂大獎#最佳歌曲|最佳歌曲]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mtv.co.uk/news/emas/163294-emas-beyonce-wins-best-song-for-halo-song |title=EMAs: Beyoncé Wins Best Song for Halo |accessdate=2010-05-19 |date=2009-11-09 |publisher=MTV UK. MTV Networks |archive-date=2012-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120129003104/http://www.mtv.co.uk/news/emas/163294-emas-beyonce-wins-best-song-for-halo-song |dead-url=no }}</ref>。这首情歌位于《{{le|Rap-Up|Rap-Up}}》2009年25大最佳歌曲名单中第7名的位置<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rap-up.com/2009/12/31/rap-ups-25-best-songs-of-2009/ |title=Rap-Up's 25 Best Songs of 2009 |work=Rap-Up |publisher=Devin Lazerine |accessdate=2011-12-11 |archive-date=2014-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141009222550/http://www.rap-up.com/2009/12/31/rap-ups-25-best-songs-of-2009/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《光环》还被提名于[[第52届格莱美奖|第52届格莱美奖]]，其中包括[[第52届格莱美奖#一般類|年度最佳录音奖]]和[[第52届格莱美奖#流行類|最佳流行女歌手]]的范畴，其赢得后者的奖项<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.grammy.com/nominees?year=2009&genre=All |title=Nominees And Winners |publisher=Grammy.com. National Academy of Recording Arts and Sciences |accessdate=2010-04-02 |date=2010-01-31 |archive-date=2010-12-19 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5v6BL72Lt?url=http://www.grammy.com/nominees?year=2009&genre=All |dead-url=no }}</ref>。它还赢得2010年克羅地亞{{le|波兰奖|Porin (music award)}}的最佳外语歌曲<ref>{{cite web |url=http://arhiva.porin.info/dobitnici-po-godinama/2010-121 |title=Porin • 2010 |publisher=Croatian Phonographic Association |accessdate=2010-03-30 |archive-date=2015-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150202204826/http://arhiva.porin.info/dobitnici-po-godinama/2010-121 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《光环》在{{le|非你莫属2009拉斯维加斯亲密接触演唱会|I Am... Yours: An Intimate Performance at Wynn Las Vegas}}的现场版本，获得了[[第53届格莱美奖|第53届格莱美奖]]的最佳流行女歌手提名<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.grammy.com/nominees?year=2010&genre=All |title=Nominees And Winners |publisher=Grammy.com. National Academy of Recording Arts and Sciences |accessdate=2011-07-06 |date=2011-02-13 |archive-date=2015-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150417051458/http://www.grammy.com/nominees?year=2010&genre=all |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.latimes.com/la-et-env-grammys-nominees-2010-list-htmlstory.html |title=Grammy Awards 2011: Winners and nominees for 53rd Grammy Awards |work=Los Angeles Times |accessdate=2017-02-26 |archive-date=2017-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170804010149/http://www.latimes.com/la-et-env-grammys-nominees-2010-list-htmlstory.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[美國作曲家、作家和發行商協會|美國作曲家、作家和發行商協會]]在第27届ASCAP流行音乐奖认可《光环》为2009年其中一首最多次播放的歌曲<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ascap.com/eventsawards/awards/popawards/2010/Most_Performed_Songs.aspx |title=Mariah Carey Wins 2010 ASCAP Pop Music Awards |publisher=American Society of Composers, Authors and Publishers |date=2010-04-20 |accessdate=2011-09-05 |archive-date=2012-07-05 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68vnL0UF2?url=http://www.ascap.com/eventsawards/awards/popawards/2010/Most_Performed_Songs.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在碧昂丝三十岁生日时，《告示牌》杂志的埃丽卡·拉米雷斯（{{lang|en|Erika Ramirez}}）和杰森·利普舒茨（{{lang|en|Jason Lipshutz}}）将这首情歌放置在碧昂丝最热门的30首《告示牌》歌曲的第18位<ref name="bill10053" />。在《乡村声音》（{{lang|en|''The Village Voice''}}）年终{{le|Pazz & Jop|Pazz & Jop}}单曲名单中，《光环》分别在2008年和2009年排在第443位和114位<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.villagevoice.com/pazznjop/singles/2008/|title=New York Pazz and Jop Singles - 2008|work=The Village Voice|publisher=Village Voice Media|accessdate=2012-03-19|archive-date=2009-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090201112814/http://www.villagevoice.com/pazznjop/singles/2008/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.villagevoice.com/pazznjop/singles/2009/|title=New York Pazz and Jop Singles - 2009|work=The Village Voice|publisher=Village Voice Media|accessdate=2012-03-19|archive-date=2010-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100326223503/http://www.villagevoice.com/pazznjop/singles/2009/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年，E!网络的约翰·布恩（{{lang|en|John Boone}}）和珍妮弗·卡迪将这首歌排在碧昂丝十大最佳歌曲的第3名，并写道其他情歌「沒有比這首歌更有力量的（情歌），碧昂絲對著那聽起來就像世界上全部樂器（其中包括超讚的一秒一次的獨奏鼓聲）的伴奏{{le|实唱|Belting (music)}}著」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://uk.eonline.com/photos/7684/top-10-best-beyonc-songs/254642|title=Top 10 Best Beyoncé Songs|first1=John|last1=Boone|first2=Jennifer|last2=Cady|publisher=E! Online. NBCUniversal|date=2013-01-30|accessdate=2013-04-28|page=8}}</ref>。[[Consequence_of_Sound|Consequence of Sound]]称《光环》为2009年最佳歌曲第23位<ref>{{cite web|url=http://consequenceofsound.net/cos-year-end-report-the-top-50-songs-of-09-25-1/|title=The Top 50 Songs of 2009|publisher=Consequence of Sound|accessdate=2017-01-06|archive-date=2017-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170107095757/http://consequenceofsound.net/cos-year-end-report-the-top-50-songs-of-09-25-1/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==上榜表现==
《光环》于2009年2月17日在美国[[告示牌百强单曲榜|《告示牌》百强单曲榜]]位于第93名<ref>{{Cite journal |page=42 |publisher=Nielsen Business Media |date=2009-02-07 |issn=0006-2510 |work=Billboard |title= Quiet Riot: How Fleet Foxes And Their Bearded Brethren Are Putting Country Comfort Into Indie Rock —And Finding Harmony On The Charts |volume=121 |issue=5}}</ref>。其于2009年5月23日在该榜单位于第5名<ref>{{Cite journal |page=42 |publisher=Nielsen Business Media |date=2009-05-23 |issn=0006-2510 |work=Billboard |title= Plus The Return Of No Doubt: How The Band Got Back Together For A Blockbuster Tour —And The Biggest Giveaway Of The Year |volume=121 |issue=20}}</ref>。这首歌使碧昂絲成為在2001至2010年的百強單曲榜上擁有最多進入排行榜前十單曲的女藝人<ref>{{cite journal |title=Don Omar: The Reggaeton Starts Plugs In For Digital Sales With 'IDon' And An iPhone App |date=2009-04-25 |work=Billboard |publisher=Nielsen Business Media |issn=0006-2510 |volume=121 |issue=16 |page=41}}</ref>。《光环》在百强单曲榜位于前40名三十个星期之后，其最后出现榜单的时间是在2009年8月29日<ref>{{Cite journal |page=54 |publisher=Nielsen Business Media |date=2009-08-29 |issn=0006-2510 |work=Billboard |title= Sean Kingston: The 'Hip-Pop' Star Has A 'Fire Burning'. Can 3-D Marketing Help Him Heat Up The Charts?|volume=121|issue=34}}</ref>。它在美国[[主流四十强音乐榜_(流行歌曲)|流行歌曲榜]]上位于第2名、在美国[[热门舞厅歌曲榜|热门舞厅歌曲榜]]位于榜首，还有在美国{{le|热门节奏蓝调/嘻哈歌曲榜|Hot R&B/Hip-Hop Songs}}上位于第16名<ref name="allmusicsingles"/>。2010年1月5日，其以销量超过两百万，被[[美國唱片業協會|美國唱片業協會]]认证为两倍白金单曲<ref name="Riaa">{{cite web|url=https://www.riaa.com/gold-platinum/?tab_active=default-award&se=Beyonce#search_section|title=RIAA certifications – Beyoncé Knowles albums|publisher=[[Recording_Industry_Association_of_America|Recording Industry Association of America]]|accessdate=2009-07-06|archive-date=2016-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160107191339/http://www.riaa.com/gold-platinum/?tab_active=default-award&se=BEYONCE#search_section|dead-url=no}}</ref>。截至2012年10月，《光环》已在美国出售3,123,000份数位销量<ref name="USsales">{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/chartbeat/474549/ask-billboard-the-twitter-sized-edition |title=Ask Billboard: The Twitter-Sized Edition |first=Gary |last=Trust |date=2012-10-20 |accessdate=2012-10-20 |work=Billboard |publisher=Prometheus Global Media |archive-date=2014-09-12 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20140912052051/http://www.billboard.com/articles/chartbeat/474549/ask-billboard-the-twitter-sized-edition |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

《光環》於2009年2月2日在[[紐西蘭單曲榜|紐西蘭單曲榜]]位於第40名，並在三星期後達到其最高排位第2名<ref name="nzz">{{cite web |url=http://charts.org.nz/showitem.asp?interpret=Beyonc%E9&titel=Halo&cat=s |title=Beyoncé - Halo (song) |publisher=Charts.org.nz. Hung Medien |accessdate=2010-06-06 |archive-date=2012-07-07 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120707084145/http://charts.org.nz/showitem.asp?interpret=Beyonc%E9&titel=Halo&cat=s |dead-url=no }}</ref>。这首歌在榜单上花费了33个非连续的星期，并以运输超过15,000的销量被[[紐西蘭唱片業協會|紐西蘭唱片業協會]]认证为白金唱片<ref name="nzcert">{{cite web |url=http://www.radioscope.net.nz/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=77&Itemid=61 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110724195845/http://www.radioscope.net.nz/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=77&Itemid=61 |archivedate=2011-07-24 |title=Latest Gold / Platinum Singles |publisher=RadioScope |accessdate=2010-12-09 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。2009年2月15日，其在[[澳大利亞單曲榜|澳大利亞單曲榜]]进入了第29名。这首情歌以四个非连续的星期位于第3名，并位于前50名而花费了36个星期<ref name="ausdeb">{{cite web |url=http://australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Beyonc%E9&titel=Halo&cat=s |title=Beyoncé - Halo (song) |publisher=Australian-charts.com. Hung Medien |accessdate=2010-06-06 |archive-date=2014-09-12 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20140912071116/http://australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Beyonc%E9&titel=Halo&cat=s |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[澳大利亞唱片業協會|澳大利亞唱片業協會]]以《光环》售卖超过280,000的销量而被认证为五倍白金唱片<ref name="auscert">{{cite web| url=http://www.aria.com.au/pages/httpwww.aria.com.aupagesaria-charts-accreditations-singles-2013.htm| title=ARIA Charts – Accreditations – 2013 Singles| publisher=[[Australian_Recording_Industry_Association|Australian Recording Industry Association]]| accessdate=2013-02-17| archive-date=2013-09-15| archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6JdeckIt9?url=http://www.aria.com.au/pages/httpwww.aria.com.aupagesaria-charts-accreditations-singles-2013.htm| dead-url=no}}</ref>。在[[西班牙单曲榜|西班牙单曲榜]]中，《光环》于2009年1月25日位于第45名，但它在之后的一周后跌落在榜单外<ref name="span">{{cite web |url=http://spanishcharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Beyonc%E9&titel=Halo&cat=s |title=Beyoncé - Halo (song) |publisher=Spanishcharts.com. Hung Medien |accessdate=2010-06-06 |archive-date=2021-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211107131538/https://spanishcharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Beyonc%E9&titel=Halo&cat=s |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而，这首歌在四个月后，也就是于2009年5月3日重回榜单中<ref name="span"/>。它以运输超过80,000的销量被[[西班牙音樂製造商協會|西班牙音樂製造商協會]]认证为两倍白金唱片<ref name="spcert">{{cite web |url=http://www.promusicae.es/listas/semanales |title=Chart: Promusicae 17 2010 |page=1 |publisher=Productores de Música de España |format=PDF |accessdate=2010-05-30 |quote=进入网站后，在「All」选择「Songs」，「Year」选择「2010」，之后按「Search Charts」，最后选择下载「TOP 50 CANCIONES 10_17」 |archive-date=2014-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140611170551/http://www.promusicae.es/listas/semanales |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

《光环》于2009年2月21日期次时在[[英国单曲排行榜|英国单曲排行榜]]位于第98名<ref name="chst">{{cite web |url=http://www.chartstats.com/songinfo.php?id=34229 |title=Beyonce – Halo |publisher=The Official Charts Company |accessdate=2010-06-06 |archive-date=2009-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090306014228/http://www.chartstats.com/songinfo.php?id=34229 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；在七个星期后，它于2009年4月4日攀升至第4名<ref name="OCC">{{cite web |url=http://www.theofficialcharts.com/archive-chart/_/1/2009-04-04/ |title=Chart Archive |publisher=The Official Charts Company |date=2009-04-04 |accessdate=2010-06-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100708194246/http://www.theofficialcharts.com/archive-chart/_/1/2009-04-04 |archivedate=2010-07-08 }}</ref>它在前100名的英国单曲排行榜里几乎呆了整年的时间；在非连续的44个星期之后，它于2012年3月4日位于第94名，接着就跌出榜单外。《光环》以售卖600,000的销量被[[英國唱片業協會|英國唱片業協會]]认证为白金唱片<ref name="ukcert">{{cite web| url=http://www.bpi.co.uk/certified-awards.aspx| title=Certified Awards Search| publisher=[[British_Phonographic_Industry|British Phonographic Industry]]| accessdate=2009-12-17| archive-date=2013-02-06| archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6EEYfYVwc?url=http://www.bpi.co.uk/certified-awards.aspx| dead-url=no}}</ref>。截至2013年7月，它在英国售卖了超过650,000的销量并成为当地第四高销量的单曲<ref name=uksalesasof2013>{{cite web|title=The Official Beyoncé and Destiny’s Child Top 40 Revealed!|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/features/the-official-beyonce-and-destinys-child-top-40-revealed-2335/|publisher=Official Charts Company|accessdate=2013-07-05|archive-date=2013-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130709002447/http://www.officialcharts.com/features/the-official-beyonce-and-destinys-child-top-40-revealed-2335/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它在首次登上[[爱尔兰单曲榜|爱尔兰单曲榜]]是2009年1月22日而位于第32名<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.chart-track.co.uk/index.jsp?c=p%2Fmusicvideo%2Fmusic%2Farchive%2Findex_test.jsp&ct=240001&arch=t&lyr=2009&year=2009&week=4 |title=Irish Singles Chart (January 22, 2009) |publisher=Chart-Track. Irish Recorded Music Association |accessdate=2012-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120516115837/http://www.chart-track.co.uk/index.jsp?c=p%2Fmusicvideo%2Fmusic%2Farchive%2Findex_test.jsp&ct=240001&arch=t&lyr=2009&year=2009&week=4 |archive-date=2012-05-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，并连续三个星期位于第4名<ref name="irl"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.chart-track.co.uk/index.jsp?c=p%2Fmusicvideo%2Fmusic%2Farchive%2Findex_test.jsp&ct=240001&arch=t&lyr=2009&year=2009&week=15 |title=Irish Singles Chart (April 16, 2009) |publisher=Chart-Track. Irish Recorded Music Association |accessdate=2012-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120614123918/http://www.chart-track.co.uk/index.jsp?c=p%2Fmusicvideo%2Fmusic%2Farchive%2Findex_test.jsp&ct=240001&arch=t&lyr=2009&year=2009&week=15 |archive-date=2012-06-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。《光环》于2009年以连续二十个星期登上巴西《[[告示牌_(杂志)|告示牌]]》[[巴西告示牌|百强热门音乐榜]]榜首<ref>{{cite web |url=http://musica.uol.com.br/ultnot/2010/02/10/beyonce-encerra-nesta-noite-em-salvador-turne-assistida-por-quase-115-mil-brasileiros.jhtm |title=Beyoncé reúne 164 mil pessoas em sua primeira turnê pelo Brasil |publisher=Universo Online. Grupo Folha |date=2010-02-07 |accessdate=2012-11-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Gm710Aag?url=http://musica.uol.com.br/ultnot/2010/02/10/beyonce-encerra-nesta-noite-em-salvador-turne-assistida-por-quase-115-mil-brasileiros.jhtm |archivedate=2013-05-21 }}</ref>。它在巴西各处的电台里超过24,734的播放而成为当时在当地电台最多播放的歌曲<ref>{{cite web |url=http://virgula.uol.com.br/home/legado/halo-de-beyonce-e-a-musica-mais-tocada-nas-radios-brasileiras-em-2009/ |title=Halo, de Beyoncé, é a música mais tocada nas rádios brasileiras em 2009 |publisher=Universo Online. Grupo Folha |date=2010-01-11 |accessdate=2012-11-16 |archive-date=2017-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170308230349/http://virgula.uol.com.br/home/legado/halo-de-beyonce-e-a-musica-mais-tocada-nas-radios-brasileiras-em-2009/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《光环》于2009年11月至2010年11月成为最多下载的歌曲，而在巴西数位音乐奖初版被作为最精彩的部分<ref name="BR Digital">{{cite web |url=http://colunas.revistaepoca.globo.com/menteaberta/2010/11/24/halo-%E2%80%93-de-beyonce-%E2%80%93-e-musica-mais-baixada-no-brasil/ |title=Halo – de Beyoncé – é música mais baixada no Brasil |work=Época |publisher=Editora Globo |date=2010-11-24 |accessdate=2012-11-16 |archive-date=2013-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130314064706/http://colunas.revistaepoca.globo.com/menteaberta/2010/11/24/halo-%e2%80%93-de-beyonce-%e2%80%93-e-musica-mais-baixada-no-brasil/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==音乐录影带==
《光环》和《玩美女神》的随附录影带首次出现是于2008年12月23日同时上传到美国的[[iTunes_Store|iTunes Store]]<ref name="ew2"/>。该录影带在2008年11月晚期拍摄于碧昂丝[[倫敦蘇荷區|倫敦蘇荷區]]所拥有的联排别墅，其由菲利普·安德尔曼（{{lang|en|Philip Andelman}}）执导并由美国演员[[麥克·艾里|麥克·艾里]]来出演碧昂丝的爱人<ref name="shot"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.theday.com/article/20111223/BIZ04/111229961 |title=Beyoncé's 'Halo' video home ready to rent for $100,000 per month |work=The Day |publisher=The Day Publishing Company |date=2011-12-23 |accessdate=2012-01-16 |archive-date=2012-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120306210638/http://www.theday.com/article/20111223/BIZ04/111229961 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="rapup1"/>。艾里非常开心能够与碧昂丝一起出演这首歌的录影带，因为当他听了这首歌后就马上就爱上它<ref name="ealy"/>。这是他第二次被邀请成为碧昂丝音乐录影带里的角色；第一次是《绝无仅有》，但是他拒绝了该邀请，因为他不喜欢它的题和概念<ref name="ealy"/>。他曾经告诉碧昂丝：「如果有一个英雄角色就打给我。」<ref name="ealy">{{cite news |url=http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2010/11/02/the-very-busy-michael-ealy-on-his-roles-in-good-wife-colored-girls-and-doing-his-own-laundry/ |work=[[The_Wall_Street_Journal|The Wall Street Journal]] |publisher=[[Dow_Jones_&_Company|Dow Jones & Company]] |accessdate=2010-11-14 |title=Michael Ealy on 'Good Wife,' 'Colored Girls', and Doing Laundry |date=2010-11-02 |first=Susan |last=Toepfer |archive-date=2011-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110829132901/http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2010/11/02/the-very-busy-michael-ealy-on-his-roles-in-good-wife-colored-girls-and-doing-his-own-laundry/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在录影带中，碧昂丝细想着那种亲密和浪漫的关系<ref name="Iamplat">{{cite video |people=[[Beyoncé|Knowles, Beyoncé]] |date=2009 |title=I Am... Sasha Fierce ''[Platinum Edition]'' |format=DVD |publisher=Columbia Records |accessdate=2011-04-12 |time=9:10 to 10:50 |url=http://www.amazon.com/Am-Sasha-Fierce-Platinum-Edition-Tracks/dp/B002LBGBR2 }}</ref>，影片开始时她依靠在墙边，亮光穿透窗户而照射在她的脸上。在其中一个场景中，碧昂丝穿着紧身的体操服，她表演这一系列的舞蹈，而她的爱人从楼厅上望着她。根据《[[娛樂周刊|娛樂周刊]]》麥可·斯萊扎克的看法，那段舞蹈动作是向1983年[[爱情片|爱情]][[电影|电影]]《{{le|闪舞|Flashdance}}》表示敬意<ref name="ew2"/>。碧昂丝和艾里之后偎依在沙发时互相含情脉脉地凝视着对方。在影片的高潮部分，碧昂丝在水底全身穿着白色，并慢慢地往上游。在副歌的开始部分，艾里亲吻了她的后颈后，她睁开了眼睛。在最后一幕时，碧昂丝躺在床上，而艾里在她的上面，那对情人面对面的互相凝视。E!網絡的珍妮弗·卡迪写道在录影带里那明亮而亮眼的光彩「让碧昂丝看起来像天使一样」<ref name="perf">{{cite web|url=http://uk.eonline.com/news/new_videos_from_beyonceacuteand_sasha/74676|title=New Videos From Beyoncé...and Sasha Fierce!|first=Jennifer|last=Cady|publisher=E! Online. NBCUniversal|date=2008-12-23|accessdate=2011-09-13|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/624yQ1ad2?url=http://www.eonline.com/news/new_videos_from_beyonceacuteand_sasha/74676|archivedate=2011-09-30|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。《[[太陽報_(英國)|太陽報]]》的艾莉森·馬洛尼（{{lang|en|Alison Maloney}}）称赞碧昂丝那「完美的形象」<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/showbiz/music/article2371187.ece|title=Star Beyonce's Halo slips|work=The Sun|publisher=News International|first=Alison|last=Maloney|date=2009-04-10|accessdate=2011-11-27|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090413013130/http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/showbiz/music/article2371187.ece|archivedate=2009-04-13}}</ref>。这个录影带被《[[黑人娛樂電視台|黑人娛樂電視台]]》列入「证明：2009年百强录影带」第72名<ref>{{cite web |author=Black Entertainment Television's |title=BET Unveils the Best 100 Music Videos of 2009 – Notarized |url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/bet-unveils-the-best-100-music-videos-of-2009---notarized-80472882.html |publisher=PR Newswire |accessdate=2011-03-09 |date=2010-01-01 |location= |archive-date=2011-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111030225831/http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/bet-unveils-the-best-100-music-videos-of-2009---notarized-80472882.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

另一版录影带于2010年5月晚期面世于网络，里面解释了碧昂丝为什么回想起在原版录影带中的爱人<ref name="rapup1"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://923now.radio.com/2010/05/27/beyonces-halo-video-version%C2%A02/|title=Beyonce's "Halo" Video, Version 2|publisher=92.3 Now Radio. CBS Radio|first=Ed|last=Easton Jr.|date=2010-05-27|accessdate=2011-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110725101308/http://923now.radio.com/2010/05/27/beyonces-halo-video-version%C2%A02/|archive-date=2011-07-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。影片开始时是在晚上和在许多树的地方，碧昂丝开着车而艾里则在森林中被警察追赶。在影片的过程中，她将车停在路边并原版的场景重现在画面中。一些[[警犬|警犬]]最终将艾里制服并残酷地攻击他。一个打开的袋子里面装着偷来的钱，那些钱被风吹得周围都是。在影片的最后，碧昂丝找到躺在地上且无生命迹象的艾里<ref name="rapup1">{{cite web |url=http://www.rap-up.com/2010/05/20/video-beyonce-halo-alternate-version/ |title=Video: Beyoncé – 'Halo' (Alternate Version) |work=Rap-Up |publisher=Devin Lazerine |accessdate=2010-06-06 |archive-date=2016-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160601083209/http://www.rap-up.com/2010/05/20/video-beyonce-halo-alternate-version/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==现场演出==
