碧昂丝于2009年2月12日在[[有色人种促进协会形象奖|有色人种促进协会形象奖]]第一次现场演唱《光环》<ref name="screen">{{cite web|url=http://www.bvnewswire.com/2009/02/12/2009-naacp-image-awards-bringing-black-star-power/|title=2009 NAACP Image Awards: Bringing Black Star Power|date=2009-02-12|publisher=Entertainment Newswire. AOL Inc|accessdate=2011-04-06|first=Brennan|last=Williams|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110911125353/http://www.bvnewswire.com/2009/02/12/2009-naacp-image-awards-bringing-black-star-power/|archivedate=2011-09-11}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/02/13/arts/13iht-peepsat.1.20173511.html|title=Anne Hathaway, Beyoncé, Jennifer Hudson|work=The New York Times|publisher=The New York Times Company|date=2009-02-13|accessdate=2011-12-19|archive-date=2017-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170630121522/http://www.nytimes.com/2009/02/13/arts/13iht-peepsat.1.20173511.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她身穿着白色礼服，当[[非裔美國人民權運動|非裔美國人民權運動]]档案画面出现背景屏幕上时演唱了这首情歌<ref name="screen"/>。娱乐通讯社（{{lang|en|Entertainment Newswire}}）的布倫南·威廉姆斯（{{lang|en|Brennan Williams}}）写道碧昂丝那「美得惊人的演出」展示了她为何会获得2009年[[有色人种促进协会形象奖|有色人种促进协会形象杰出女艺人奖]]<ref name="screen"/>。她还于2009年4月22日在[[大卫·莱特曼晚间秀|大卫·莱特曼晚间秀]]演唱《光环》<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rap-up.com/2009/04/22/beyonce-holds-her-own-umbrella/#more-16486 |title=Beyoncé Holds Her Own Umbrella |work=Rap-Up |publisher=Devin Lazerine |date=2009-04-22 |accessdate=2009-08-16 |archive-date=2009-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090428133355/http://www.rap-up.com/2009/04/22/beyonce-holds-her-own-umbrella/#more-16486 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/beyonce-puts-rumors-to-rest-with-fierce-letterman-performance-20090423|title=Beyonce Puts Rumors to Rest With Fierce "Letterman" Performance|work=Rolling Stone|publisher=Wenner Media LLC|date=2009-04-23|accessdate=2011-11-28|archive-date=2012-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121229221625/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/beyonce-puts-rumors-to-rest-with-fierce-letterman-performance-20090423|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并在接着的一天于[[今天_(NBC)|今日秀]]中表演<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/beyonce-calls-today-show-singing-scandal-ridiculous-20090422|work=Rolling Stone|publisher=Wenner Media LLC|date=2009-04-22|title=Beyonce Calls 'Today' Show Singing Scandal 'Ridiculous'|accessdate=2011-03-29|archive-date=2012-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120208104735/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/beyonce-calls-today-show-singing-scandal-ridiculous-20090422|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这首歌之后加进了她的2009年至2010年{{le|双面碧昂丝巡回演唱会|I Am... Tour}}的曲目列表里<ref name="indep">{{Cite news |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/reviews/beyonc-02-arena-london-1691069.html |title=Beyoncé, 02 Arena, London |date=2009-05-27 |accessdate=2010-05-21 |work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]] |publisher=Independent Print Limited |first=Alice |last=Jones |archive-date=2012-01-30 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/655XixTF1?url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/reviews/beyonc-02-arena-london-1691069.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="rolltour">{{cite web|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/beyonce-brings-hits-jay-z-to-i-am-tour-opener-in-new-york-20090622|title=Beyonce Brings Hits, Jay-Z to 'I Am...' Tour opener in New York|accessdate=2011-03-29|date=2009-06-22|work=Rolling Stone|publisher=Wenner Media LLC|archive-date=2012-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120817000624/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/beyonce-brings-hits-jay-z-to-i-am-tour-opener-in-new-york-20090622|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而它则作为演唱会的[[安可|安可]]歌曲来表演<ref name="indep"/><ref name="rolltour"/>。在碧昂丝完成演出《單身女郎(定情戒)》之后，她演唱《光环》。她在走向前排的观众并与他们握手之前演唱了这首情歌<ref name="rolltour"/>。《{{le|贝尔法斯特电讯报|Belfast Telegraph}}》的黛博拉·麥卡利斯（{{lang|en|Deborah McAleese}}）和劳伦·马尔文尼（{{lang|en|Lauren Mulvenny}}）回应道这首情歌是「以强烈的情感来演唱」<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/entertainment/music/news/in-pictures--beyonc-in-belfast-14321526.html |title=In Pictures: Beyoncé in Belfast |first1=Deborah |last1=McAleese |first2=Lauren |last2=Mulvenny |date=2009-06-01 |accessdate=2011-01-11 |work=The Belfast Telegraph |publisher=Independent News & Media |archive-date=2011-04-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110426193234/http://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/entertainment/music/news/in-pictures--beyonc-in-belfast-14321526.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。它还包括在非你莫属2009拉斯维加斯亲密接触演唱会的CD/DVD的现场专辑<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1625283/beyonce-host-thanksgiving-special.jhtml|title=Beyonce To Host Thanksgiving Special|publisher=MTV News. MTV Networks|first=Gil|last=Kaufman|date=2009-11-02|accessdate=2011-11-28|archive-date=2012-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120622091357/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1625283/beyonce-host-thanksgiving-special.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>和2010年的{{le|双面碧昂丝世界巡回演唱会|I Am... World Tour}}里<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.amazon.de/I-Am-World-Tour-Blu-ray/dp/B0046MOV8U |title=I Am...World Tour |publisher=Amazon (Germany) |accessdate=2010-11-15 |archive-date=2013-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014001329/http://www.amazon.de/I-Am-World-Tour-Blu-ray/dp/B0046MOV8U |dead-url=no }}</ref>。碧昂丝在[[格拉斯顿伯里当代表演艺术节|2011年格拉斯顿伯里艺术节]]将《光环》作为闭幕歌曲表演，而当时观看演出的观众有超过175,000人<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mtv.co.uk/news/beyonce/279275-beyonce-glastonbury-jay-z-coldplay-chris-martin |title=Beyoncé Closes 2011 Glastonbury Festival |publisher=MTV UK. MTV Networks |date=2011-06-27 |accessdate=2011-08-10 |archive-date=2011-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110801002553/http://www.mtv.co.uk/news/beyonce/279275-beyonce-glastonbury-jay-z-coldplay-chris-martin |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[独立电视台|独立电视台]]特别节目「与碧昂丝共度夜晚」中，她与被抽选的粉丝共同演唱那首情歌，而该节目于2011年12月4日在英国播出<ref>{{cite video|people=Knowles, Beyoncé|date=December 4, 2011|title=A Night With Beyoncé|medium=ITV1 video|publisher=Victory Television Network in co-production with Sony Music Entertainment|location=The Fountain Studios, London, United Kingdom|time=9pm|id=|isbn=|oclc=}}</ref>。

2009年6月25日，美国艺人[[麥可·傑克森|麥可·傑克森]]在碧昂丝巡回时[[迈克尔·杰克逊之死|逝世]]<ref name="b events"/>。他的死亡消息让她在到达巡回地点表演时对杰克森表示哀悼，这其中包括2009年7月1日在[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]][[亚特兰大|亚特兰大]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.michaeljackson.com/us/news/beyonce-performs-sensational-tribute-michael-jackson-atlanta |title=Beyonce Performs A Sensational Tribute To Michael Jackson In Atlanta |date=November 23, 2010 |publisher=Michael Jackson Official Website. Sony Music Entertainment |accessdate=2010-06-07 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/624yH8xMI?url=http://www.michaeljackson.com/us/news/beyonce-performs-sensational-tribute-michael-jackson-atlanta |archivedate=2011-09-30 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="b events">{{cite web|url=http://beyonceonline.com/us/events|title=Events|accessdate=2010-06-07|publisher=Beyoncé Official Website. Columbia Records|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090211185107/http://beyonceonline.com/us/events|archivedate=2009-02-11}}</ref>和2009年7月3日在[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]][[紐奧良|紐奧良]]<ref name="mtvmj">{{cite web |publisher=MTV UK. MTV Networks |url=http://www.mtv.co.uk/news/beyonce/131404-beyonce-michael-jackson |title=Beyoncé Pays Tribute To Michael Jackson |date=2009-07-07 |accessdate=2010-05-21 |archive-date=2012-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121021140406/http://www.mtv.co.uk/news/beyonce/131404-beyonce-michael-jackson |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在哀悼中，杰克森的影像展示在主屏幕里。碧昂丝以情绪化的方式来演唱《光环》，并更改歌词为「Michael I can see your Halo / I pray your music won't fade away」（大意：麥可我看見你身上散發的光環/我祈祷你的音乐永远不会消逝）<ref name="mtvmj"/>。2010年1月12日，[[海地|海地]]因[[2010年海地地震|地震]]而受到重创。[[慈善组织|募捐马拉松电视节目]]{{le|送希望到海地：全球赈灾义演|Hope for Haiti Now: A Global Benefit for Earthquake Relief}}于2010年1月22日举行，当中有许多艺人参与其中，而当中包括碧昂丝<ref name="haitilive">{{cite web |url=http://newsroom.mtv.com/2010/01/22/hope-for-haiti-live-blog/ |date=January 22, 2010 |title=Hope For Haiti Now: A Global Benefit For Earthquake Relief |first=Kyle |last=Anderson |publisher=MTV News. MTV Networks |accessdate=May 25, 2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100311001429/http://newsroom.mtv.com/2010/01/22/hope-for-haiti-live-blog |archivedate=2010年3月11日 }}</ref><ref name="usatoday5">{{Cite news |url=http://content.usatoday.com/communities/entertainment/post/2010/01/george-clooney-explains-hope-for-haiti-celebrity-phone-bank/1 |title=George Clooney explains 'Hope for Haiti' celebrity phone bank |first=Ann |last=Oldenburg |work=[[USA_Today|USA Today]] |publisher=Gannett Company |date=January 22, 2010 |accessdate=2010-05-25 |archive-date=2012-07-07 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120707154533/http://content.usatoday.com/communities/entertainment/post/2010/01/george-clooney-explains-hope-for-haiti-celebrity-phone-bank/1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她在慈善中演唱《光环》的[[原音乐|原音版本]]，而[[酷玩乐团|酷玩乐团]]主唱[[克里斯·馬汀|克里斯·馬汀]]则演奏钢琴<ref name="haitilive"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1630334/beyonce-performs-halo-with-chris-martin-during-haiti-telethon.jhtml|title=Beyonce Performs 'Halo' With Chris Martin During Haiti Telethon|publisher=MTV News. MTV Networks|first=Hillary|last=Crosley|date=2011-01-22|accessdate=2011-11-27|archive-date=2014-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140203045702/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1630334/beyonce-performs-halo-with-chris-martin-during-haiti-telethon.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。为了让这首歌更符合当晚的目的<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://artsbeat.blogs.nytimes.com/2010/01/23/in-song-trying-to-convey-the-scope-of-a-tragedy/|title=In Song, Trying to Convey the Scope of a Tragedy|work=The New York Times|publisher=The New York Times Company|first=Jon|last=Caramanica|date=2010-01-23|accessdate=2011-12-19|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6FMigzwFJ?url=http://artsbeat.blogs.nytimes.com/2010/01/23/in-song-trying-to-convey-the-scope-of-a-tragedy/|archivedate=2013-03-24|deadurl=yes}}</ref>，碧昂丝将「海地」放入歌词中，并唱道：「Haiti, we can see your halo / You know you're my saving grace / You're everything I need and more, it's written all over your face / Haiti, we can see your halo / I pray you won't fade away」（大意：海地，我们看见你的光环/知道吗，你就是我的守护天使/你是我所需要的一切，甚至更多，這全都寫在了你的臉上/海地，我们看见你的光环/我祈禱你永遠不會消逝）<ref name="weave"/>。这个版本包含在2010年现场专辑《{{le|送希望到海地|Hope for Haiti Now (album)}}》<ref name="weave">{{cite web |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1630348/20100122/rihanna.jhtml |title='Hope For Haiti Now' Performances: A Track-By-Track List |date=2010-01-22 |accessdate=2010-05-25 |publisher=MTV News. MTV Networks |archive-date=2010-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100324224438/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1630348/20100122/rihanna.jhtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2012年2月11日，美国歌手[[惠妮·休斯頓|惠妮·休斯頓]]逝世。在她死后，碧昂丝于2012年5月在[[大西洋城|大西洋城]]{{le|芮維爾賭場|TEN Atlantic City}}的{{le|芮維爾呈现：碧昂丝现场表演|Revel Presents: Beyoncé Live}}中向休斯敦致敬<ref name="ewtribute" /><ref name="village">{{cite web|url=http://blogs.villagevoice.com/music/2012/05/beyonce_ovation_revel_may_26_review.php|title=Live: Beyoncé Brings The House Down At Atlantic City's Newest Casino|work=The Village Voice|publisher=Village Voice Media|first=Maura|last=Johnston|date=2012-05-27|accessdate=2012-06-23|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120529031543/http://blogs.villagevoice.com/music/2012/05/beyonce_ovation_revel_may_26_review.php|archivedate=2012-05-29}}</ref>。碧昂丝身穿红色裙子<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.spin.com/articles/run-world-showgirls-beyonce-gets-back-business-atlantic-city|title=Run the World (Showgirls): Beyonce Gets Back to Business in Atlantic City|work=Spin|publisher=Spin Media LLC|first=Caryn|last=Ganz|date=2012-05-29|accessdate=June 23, 2012-06-23|archive-date=2012-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120604070805/http://www.spin.com/articles/run-world-showgirls-beyonce-gets-back-business-atlantic-city|dead-url=no}}</ref>，她开始《光环》的演出并演唱惠妮·休斯頓《[[我将永远爱你|我将永远爱你]]》的首节<ref name="village" />。《{{le|乡村声音报|The Village Voice}}》的莫拉·約翰斯頓（{{lang|en|Maura Johnston}}）赞赏演出值得注意之處是这首歌「提供一个突然迸發的结尾」而展示了如何「由流行界其中一位最能削平模版的词曲作家创作的最基本结构的歌曲……但在对的歌手中可以将它转变成极为美丽的东西」<ref name="village" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/the-juice/485663/beyonce-returns-to-the-stage-in-atlantic-city|title=Beyonce Returns to the Stage in Atlantic City|work=Billboard|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|first=Erika|last=Ramirez|date=2012-05-29|accessdate=2012-06-21|archive-date=2013-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130203223540/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/the-juice/485663/beyonce-returns-to-the-stage-in-atlantic-city|dead-url=no}}</ref>。当评论这场表演时，《娱乐周刊》的凯尔·安德森（{{lang|en|Kyle Anderson}}）写道「当晚最能吸引眼球的时刻……特别是当她浸入其他艺人的目录里。」<ref name="ewtribute">{{cite web|url=http://music-mix.ew.com/2012/05/29/beyonce-concerts-atlantic-city-covers/|title=Beyonce's post-baby concerts: Whitney Houston tribute, Goo Goo Dolls and Lauryn Hill songs|work=Entertainment Weekly|publisher=Time Inc|first=Kyle|last=Anderson|date=2012-05-29|accessdate=2012-06-23|archive-date=2012-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120602070954/http://music-mix.ew.com/2012/05/29/beyonce-concerts-atlantic-city-covers/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>《纽约时报》的本·拉特利夫（{{lang|en|Ben Ratliff}}）表演这首歌在表演中「几乎达到最高点」<ref name="nytimes">{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/05/27/arts/music/beyonces-return-to-stage-is-a-return-to-familiar-form.html?|title=Beyoncé: Coming Back and Catching Up, Then Conquering|work=The New York Times|publisher=The New York Times Company|first=Ben|last=Ratliff|date=2012-05-27|accessdate=2012-06-21|archive-date=2012-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120601222841/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/05/27/arts/music/beyonces-return-to-stage-is-a-return-to-familiar-form.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年2月3日，碧昂丝在{{le|第四十七屆超級盃中場表演|Super Bowl XLVII halftime show}}中表演了这首歌<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nj.com/entertainment/index.ssf/2013/02/beyonce_halftime_show_super_bo.html|title=Beyonce halftime show at Super Bowl 2013: Plenty to prove|publisher=New Jersey On-Line LLC.|date=2013-02-03|accessdate=2013-02-03|first=Tris|last=McCall|archive-date=2013-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130206212502/http://www.nj.com/entertainment/index.ssf/2013/02/beyonce_halftime_show_super_bo.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《光环》加进{{le|卡特夫人秀世界巡迴演唱会|The Mrs. Carter Show World Tour}}的表演曲目里<ref>{{cite web|title=Beyoncé makes nod to The Verve at London's O2 Arena|url=http://www.nme.com/news/beyonce/70022|work=NME|publisher=IPC Media|accessdate=2013-05-08|archive-date=2013-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130509032201/http://www.nme.com/news/beyonce/70022|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

