20100923074824/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/8344241.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美国歌手[[麥克·波斯納|麥克·波斯納]]也翻唱了这首情歌，但使用了不同的歌词，并放在他2009年的专辑《{{le|时间的问题|A Matter of Time (Mike Posner mixtape)}}》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/957614/duke-grad-mike-posner-heats-up-the-charts|title=Duke Grad Mike Posner Heats Up The Charts|work=Billboard|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|first=Gail|last=Mitchell|date=2010-06-25|accessdate=2011-11-30|archive-date=2013-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130523053150/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/957614/duke-grad-mike-posner-heats-up-the-charts|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="posner">{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/music/artist/posner_mike_4_/artist.jhtml#biographyEnd|title=Mike Posner – Artist Biography|publisher=MTV. MTV Networks|accessdate=2011-11-30|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111126171854/http://www.mtv.com/music/artist/posner_mike_4_/artist.jhtml#biographyEnd|archivedate=2011-11-26}}</ref>。根据MTV专栏作家的看法，伯纳斯的表现手法「比起原版是令人耳目一新的风格」<ref name="posner" />。大卫·赛迪斯（{{lang|en|David Sides}}）也制作了歌曲的钢琴版本并放进他专辑《歌曲收集第3卷》（{{lang|en|''The Collection, Vol. 3''}}）里来发行<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/the-collection-volume-3/id1052863338|title=The Collection, Vol. 3 by David Sides|publisher=iTunes Store. Apple Inc|accessdate=2012-05-25|archive-date=2017-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170312082037/https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/the-collection-volume-3/id1052863338|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《光环》同时出现在英国[[合辑|合辑专辑]]《{{le|现在這就是我所說的音樂！73 (英國系列)|Now That's What I Call Music! 73 (UK series)|现在！73}}》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/now-thats-what-i-call-music!-73-uk-mw0001316534|title=now thats what i call music! 73 uk|publisher=AllMusic|accessdate=2009-07-07|archive-date=2016-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160704205313/http://www.allmusic.com/album/now-thats-what-i-call-music%21-73-uk-mw0001316534|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这首歌被[[爱尔兰|爱尔兰]][[男子音乐组合|男子音乐组合]][[西域男孩|西域男孩]]与《如何让我心碎》（{{lang|en|''How to Break a Heart''}}）[[混搭_(音樂)|混搭]]，并在他们2010年[[这就是我们巡回演唱会_(西域男孩)|这就是我们巡回演唱会]]中演出<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/entertainment/music/news/belfast-goes-crazy-for-westlife-28534084.html |title=Belfast goes crazy for Westlife |work=Belfast Telegraph |date=2010-05-13 |accessdate=2017-03-11 |first=Andrew |last=Johnston |archive-date=2016-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160822110329/http://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/entertainment/music/news/belfast-goes-crazy-for-westlife-28534084.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012年2月5日，澳大利亚达人秀《{{le|年轻才艺时间秀|Young Talent Time}}》团体演唱了这首歌做为当晚的闭幕曲<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.take40.com/news/28867/16-year-old-anja-wows-the-audience-with-cold-chisel-classic-on-young-talent-time! |title=16 Year-Old Anja Wows The Audience With Cold Chisel Classic On Young Talent Time |work=Take 40 Australia |publisher=MCM Entertainment |date=2012-02-05 |accessdate=2012-04-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004223352/http://www.take40.com/news/28867/16-year-old-anja-wows-the-audience-with-cold-chisel-classic-on-young-talent-time%21 |archivedate=2013-10-04 }}</ref>。2013年4月17日，《[[美国偶像|美国偶像]]》第12季的参赛选手{{le|安琪·米勒|Angie Miller (American singer)}}在节目的其中一集中翻唱了这首歌<ref name="angie">{{cite web|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/videos/american-idol-recap-candice-glover-steals-the-show-again-20130418|title='American Idol' Recap: Candice Glover Steals the Show Again|work=Rolling Stone|publisher=Wenner Media|first=Melissa|last=Locker|date=2013-04-18|accessdate=2013-04-19|archive-date=2013-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130420100049/http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/videos/american-idol-recap-candice-glover-steals-the-show-again-20130418|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[滚石杂志|滚石杂志]]》的梅丽莎·洛克（{{lang|en|Melissa Locker}}）回应这场表演为是她「最棒的表演」和「成功在没有钢琴的情况下注入歌曲中的力量」<ref name="angie" />。

