{{le|爱永无止境 (贾梅尼·道格拉斯专辑)|Love Never Fails (Jahméne Douglas album)|爱永无止境}}》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5020399/x-factor-star-jahmene-douglas-leads-uk-albums-chart-as-now-comp-smashes-300000|title='X Factor' Star Jahmene Douglas Leads U.K. Albums Chart as 'Now' Comp Smashes 300,000 Sales|work=Billboard|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|first=Paul|last=Sexton|date=2013-07-29|accessdate=2013-08-22|archive-date=2013-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130811233354/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5020399/x-factor-star-jahmene-douglas-leads-uk-albums-chart-as-now-comp-smashes-300000|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年9月，[[印度|印度]]歌手{{le|桑妮蒂·喬寒|Sunidhi Chauhan}}在[[伦敦|伦敦]][[皇家阿爾伯特音樂廳|皇家阿爾伯特音樂廳]]翻唱这首歌。《[[印度时报|印度时报]]》的专栏作家称这首歌的演出是整场演唱会中最精彩的部分<ref>{{cite news|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/music/news-and-interviews/Sunidhi-mesmerizes-audiences-with-Beyonces-Halo/articleshow/23577704.cms|title=Sunidhi mesmerizes audiences with Beyonce’s Halo|work=[[The_Times_of_India|The Times of India]]|publisher=The Times Group|date=2013-10-06|accessdate=2013-10-06|archive-date=2016-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160125172808/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/music/news-and-interviews/Sunidhi-mesmerizes-audiences-with-Beyonces-Halo/articleshow/23577704.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[福克斯廣播公司|福克斯廣播公司]]电视节目《[[欢乐合唱团|欢乐合唱团]]》其中一集《{{le|维他命D (欢乐合唱团)|Vitamin D (Glee)|维他命D}}》将《光环》和[[卡翠娜与波浪乐团|卡翠娜与波浪乐团]]1985年歌曲《{{le|走在阳光里|Walking on Sunshine (Katrina and the Waves song)}}》混搭在一起表演<ref>{{cite press release|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/network-press-releases/glee-rules-the-itunes-charts-with-astounding-1-1-million-downloads/|title='Glee' rules the iTunes charts with astounding 1.1 million downloads|publisher=Fox Entertainment Group. Fox Broadcasting Company|date=2009-10-06|accessdate=2010-05-19|archive-date=2017-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170308222943/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/network-press-releases/glee-rules-the-itunes-charts-with-astounding-1-1-million-downloads/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。其后这个版本以单曲方式发行，其在爱尔兰单曲榜位于第4名<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.chart-track.co.uk/index.jsp?c=p%2Fmusicvideo%2Fmusic%2Farchive%2Findex_test.jsp&ct=240001&arch=t&lyr=2010&year=2010&week=6 |title=Irish Singles Chart (February 11, 2010) |publisher=Chart-Track. Irish Recorded Music Association |accessdate=2012-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111107011956/http://www.chart-track.co.uk/index.jsp?c=p%2Fmusicvideo%2Fmusic%2Farchive%2Findex_test.jsp&ct=240001&arch=t&lyr=2010&year=2010&week=6 |archive-date=2011-11-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，在英国单曲下载榜位于第8名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/archive-chart/_/6/2010-02-27/ |title=Chart Archive |publisher=The Official Charts Company |date=2010-02-27 |accessdate=2013-03-24}}</ref>，在英国单曲榜位于第9名<ref name="gleeuk">{{cite web |url=http://www.theofficialcharts.com/archive-chart/_/1/2010-02-20/ |title=Chart Archive |publisher=The Official Charts Company |accessdate=2011-07-08 |date=2010-02-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111026084236/http://www.theofficialcharts.com/archive-chart/_/1/2010-02-20/ |archivedate=2011-10-26 }}</ref>，在澳大利亚唱片业协会单曲榜位于第10名<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ultratop.be/nl/showitem.asp?interpret=Glee+Cast&titel=Halo+%2F+Walking+On+Sunshine&cat=s |title=Glee Cast – Halo / Walking On Sunshine |publisher=Ultratop. Hung Medien |accessdate=2010-12-12 |archive-date=2012-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121026023936/http://www.ultratop.be/nl/showitem.asp?interpret=Glee+Cast&titel=Halo+%2F+Walking+On+Sunshine&cat=s |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在[[加拿大百强单曲榜|加拿大百强单曲榜]]位于第28名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/2009-10-24/canadian-hot-100?order=gainer |work=Billboard |publisher=Nielsen Business Media |title=Week of October 24, 2009 |date=2009-10-24 |accessdate=2011-01-17}}</ref>和在美国百强单曲榜位于第40名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/2009-10-24/hot-100?order=gainer |work=Billboard |publisher=Nielsen Business Media |title=Week of October 24, 2009 |date=2009-10-24 |accessdate=2011-01-20}}</ref>。其以运输超过35,000的销量被澳大利亚唱片业协会认证为金唱片<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.aria.com.au/pages/httpwww.aria.com.auaccreds2010.htm| title=ARIA Charts – Accreditations – 2010 Singles| publisher=Australian Recording Industry Association| accessdate=2010-12-12| archive-date=2015-05-09| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150509002236/http://aria.com.au/pages/httpwww.aria.com.auaccreds2010.htm| dead-url=no}}</ref>。这首混搭歌曲包含在2010-2011年度{{le|欢乐合唱团现场直播！在演唱会！|Glee Live! In Concert!}}的表演曲目<ref>{{cite web |url=http://blog.zap2it.com/frominsidethebox/2010/05/glee-tour-set-list-peek-bad-romance-push-it-vocal-adrenaline.html |title='Glee' tour set list peek: 'Bad Romance,' 'Push It,' Vocal Adrenaline |last=Nguyen |first=Hanh |date=2010-05-17 |publisher=Zap2it. Tribune Media Services |accessdate=2011-12-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6AIamh8n1?url=http://blog.zap2it.com/frominsidethebox/2010/05/glee-tour-set-list-peek-bad-romance-push-it-vocal-adrenaline.html |archivedate=2012-08-30 }}</ref>。《光环》还包含于[[艾美奖|艾美]]赢家巴西肥皂剧《{{le|印度之路|Caminho das Índias}}》的国际原声带<ref name="Som Livre">{{cite web|url=http://www.somlivre.com/?1630/produto/CD/Caminho-das-Indias-Internacional/Varios---Caminho-das-Indias|publisher=Som Livre|title=Caminho Das Índias Soundtrack|accessdate=2010-06-14|archive-date=2011-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716104448/http://www.somlivre.com/?1630%2Fproduto%2FCD%2FCaminho-das-Indias-Internacional%2FVarios---Caminho-das-Indias|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

